comments: House Jr. (HOU) makes marginal contact with Schroder's (OKC) body during his shooting motion that does not affect the driving shot attempt.

Dort (OKC) is late to the spot and makes contact with Harden (HOU) which affects his SQBR on his drive to the basket.  Harden braces for the oncoming contact and does not extends his arm to deliver contact.
Schroder (OKC) makes marginal contact with Harden (HOU) during the drive.
Capela (HOU) collapses his arm, jumps vertically and absorbs contact from Schroder (OKC) when contact occurs on the driving shot attempt.
Schroder (OKC) is beat to the spot and turns his body into Harden (HOU) and makes contact to his arm which affects his ability to maintain control of the ball.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) makes some contact with House Jr. (HOU) during his driving shot attempt but the contact is marginal.
Harden (HOU) and Schroder (OKC) briefly engage and separate during the inbound.
Schroder (OKC) initiates contact with Harden (HOU) during the inbound but the contact is marginal.
Paul (OKC) is not in a legal guarding position when he makes contact with Westbrook (HOU) that affects his SQBR.
Capela (HOU) sets the pick in Paul's (OKC) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Muscala (OKC) retreats from contact and is in a legal vertical position when he absorbs contact from Westbrook (HOU) during the driving shot attempt.
House Jr. (HOU) extends his foot and trips Schroder's (OKC).
Capela (HOU) and Paul (OKC) make incidental contact during rebounding.
Gallinari (OKC) places a marginal forearm to Harden's (HOU) front during the drive before removing the contact.
Harden (HOU) makes contact with Gallinari (OKC) during his driving shot attempt but the contact is marginal.
Paul (OKC) reaches in and makes marginal contact to Westbrook's (OKC) front.  The contact does not affect his SQBR and he then loses the ball on his own.
Muscala (OKC) legally contests Westbrook's (HOU) jump shot attempt.
Capela (HOU) is firming up in a screening position in Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path when contact occurs and Capela does not prevent him from disengaging from the contact.
House Jr. (HOU) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
House Jr. (HOU) slightly extends his leg during his shooting motion on the jump shot attempt and the contact with Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) is marginal.
